title: Benched with Bonnetta: Picking a new team with Marc Sessler
itunes:title: Benched with Bonnetta: Picking a new team with Marc Sessler
description:
Rachel Bonnetta and company are back for a brand new episode of Benched with Bonnetta, featuring Marc Sessler! Rachel and Marc start by reacting to the Deshaun Watson settlement. Then, Rachel asks Marc for his thoughts on a series of random things, including Tik Tok and She-Hulk (14:18). After the break, the hosts discuss the best (and worst) things they've seen or heard recently (20:38), and finally, Rachel narrows the Benched Bachelorette competition down to the final three teams to prepare for the three-part Benched Bachelorette finale (26:48).

Note: timecodes approximate.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
